summary:
The available literature does not support an association between aberrant loss of Dickkopf-3 and lymph node metastasis in gastric cancer. No studies were found indicating that DKK3 could serve as a predictor for lymph node dissemination preoperatively.

\boxed{\text{No}}

The summary focuses only on clinically significant findings related directly to predicting lymph node metastasis through DKK3 levels. It avoids speculative interpretations beyond what was explicitly supported by retrieval results.

